content: Now that you have arrived at the present day, it's time to start thinking about the future. The next logical step would be to craft a vision for your future as a musician, and to map out a plan for how you will achieve your goals. This could involve setting specific, measurable, attainable, relevant, and time-bound (SMART) goals, as well as outlining the steps you will take to reach those goals. Additionally, you might consider the kind of impact you want to have on the world through your music, and what kind of legacy you want to leave. This can be a powerful motivator, and can help you stay focused and driven as you work towards your dreams.
